===Etymology===
From the Sanskrit

===Noun=== <!--Platts gives s.m. as the POS mark, I'll have to dig for what that is-->
'''आसन''' (āsan) {{m}}
#sitting
#mode of sitting, posture, attitude, position
#seat, place, stool
#a small carpet or deer-skin on which Hindūs sit during prayer

